### ========================================
### EXERCISE 04 - Required Query Tests
### ========================================

### 1. Get all tickets (no filter)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets

### 2. Filter by status = OPEN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?status=OPEN

### 3. Filter by priority = HIGH
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?priority=HIGH

### 4. Filter by category = Email
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?category=Email

### 5. Paged tickets - first page
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/paged?page=0&size=5

### 6. Paged tickets - second page
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/paged?page=1&size=5

### 7. Paged tickets sorted by createdAt descending
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/paged?page=0&size=5&sortBy=createdAt&direction=desc

